rows.label: qst701903_msg0001
rows.name: Well, hello darlings. How's it going?

rows.label: qst701903_msg0002
rows.name:
I heard you're a big deal now.
Are you here to kill time, or is
this another sweet job for me?

rows.label: qst701903_msg0003
rows.name:
...What? You want me to
take you to Invidia?

rows.label: qst701903_msg0004
rows.name:
Hmm... alright. I owe
you one, after all.

rows.label: qst701903_msg0005
rows.name:
And it seems the old master and
Wotta are in your debt as well.

rows.label: qst701903_msg0006
rows.name:
So, let me get this straight...
First to Aletta, to pick up your
friends and drop them in Invidia.

rows.label: qst701903_msg0007
rows.name:
Then, when they're done,
I bring them back to
Aletta. That about right?

rows.label: qst701903_msg0008
rows.name:
Roger that. I'll start preparations right
away. Come to the Aletta port after you've
had a good night's sleep or two, okay?

rows.label: qst701903_msg0101
rows.name: All this for one little girl, huh?

rows.label: qst701903_msg0102
rows.name:
They all looked so full of life.
You've got some good friends.
